The paper discusses overfitting in multiclass prediction problems, which is a topic closely related to machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also presents theoretical bounds and practical attacks, which involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
